{"tid":1282113,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急]香港有情緒傳染病 大撚鍋","createTime":"2019-07-03T13:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T13:43:18.000Z","uid":271085,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9d6ab3a713bdbfdf5fa4681dba4169ae977cf99e","tid":1282113,"uid":271085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:13:16.000Z","msg":"自從梁兄弟嘅犧牲事件 一星期至少一個因為政治問題死一個人 今日先有幾個差啲跳左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢件事只會愈黎愈嚴重 呢個係一個傳情緒傅染病 <br />\n<br />\n「維特效應」（Werther Effect）不僅可以預測自殺的增加 而且大部分自殺方式將以與被報導的自殺做法相同或類似<br />\n<br />\n能夠抵消「維特效應」的就是「巴巴吉諾效應」（Papageno effect）意指媒體可以預防自殺行為 當媒體拒絕宣傳自殺事件或改變他們提供自殺事件信息的方式時 模仿自殺的風險就會下降(Source: International Journal of Environmental Research and Public Health,  Scientific American, Open Access Government)<br />\n<br />\n所以話呼籲巴絲唔好再大肆宣傳三位兄弟姊妹嘅壯烈犧牲 心中有佢地就得 同埋唔好再叫&rdquo;烈士&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n仲有 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚以為犧牲就有用啊</span></strong></span> 屌你地老母 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">留翻條命 同佢地鬥長命 死嘅唔應該係你地 係個仆街政府啊屌</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好再要我地擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89d65743dacc89962e196119c4fdf408b6116f9","tid":1282113,"uid":9076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11